{"tid":229271,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"郭文貴: 中資能掌控香港經濟 多派移民過去 香港01 : 海底撈福利好","createTime":"2017-05-04T13:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T17:07:18.000Z","uid":49359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e0e59eb58b6734cffdc5f2a4117c001a9b01a14","tid":229271,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:03:29.000Z","msg":"海底撈都講開好耐<br />\n郭文貴單野爆出來就係到吹奏中資<br />\n怪唔得好多巴打都話01係小罵大幫忙<br />\n連登個吹奏POST第一頁第一個提中資福利好<br />\n之前就吹奏過移民大陸<br />\n今次郭文貴單野都好重視<br />\n用左唔少打手<br />\n<br />\n最後講唔好太短視<br />\n半年我記得就有兩單新聞<br />\n中資最後會真係請香港人?<br />\n就連左派團體之前都話用返大陸人<br />\n香港班土共都俾人當避孕套<br />\n<br />\n中飛內地工程師佔半數 考試易過本地人<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161125/55965218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161125%2F55965218&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=40162eba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161125%2F55965218&h=80a21600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161125/55965218</a><br />\n中飛新編更制度唔覆當應承 李卓人批霸王硬上弓<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161125/55965041\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161125%2F55965041&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d8c3f926\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161125%2F55965041&h=788277f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161125/55965041</a><br />\n<br />\n樂香園：中資行賤招逼走港人<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20160606/19642744\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20160606%2F19642744&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=680be54d\" data-ef-url=\"https://e